, there were once four such sins.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you youngsters\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"four such sins\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Look it up.)\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, that is precisely what the Decalogue is all about.\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2590, \"end\": 2599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ten_Commandments\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4457514066302503e-27, \"text\": \"Decalogue\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ten_Commandments\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ten_Commandments\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"precisely what\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exactly the reason why religion classes no longer teach them.\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Exactly the reason\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"religion classes\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, some of them do.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But you can count them on one hand.\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one hand\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This new irenicism-on-steroids is daily reinforced by liturgies eliciting as much fervor and passion for God as the weekly Ladies Auxiliary canasta club.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This new irenicism\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"steroids\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"liturgies\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"as much fervor\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"passion\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \